[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m For each patient in the cohort, the pipeline produces a fitted trajectory through the observed history and a forward forecast under "current treatment continued." The forecast carries credible intervals at every horizon point; uncertainty is the product, not a footnote. The same step computes the time-to-endpoint distribution by Monte Carlo sampling from the forecast posterior.
