[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Combines slope uncertainty propagated through m_target,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     intercept uncertainty, observation noise, and (when applicable)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     treatment-effect modifier uncertainty derived from the trial
