[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             continue
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         prior = model.trial_priors.get(tx["drug_class"])
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         if not prior:
